  "description": [
    "LEGAL NOTICES NOTICE TO CONTRACTORS Notice is hereby given that sealed will be received and publicly bids opened and read at 10 A M MST Aug ust 4 1950 by the State Board of Ex aminers at their office in the Capitol Building Helena Montana for the en largement of pipe tunnels under the State Board of Health Building Capitol grounds Helena Montana Bid shall be made on the Bid Pro posal attached to the specifications Specifications may be obtained from the Engineer for the State Board of Ex aminers Capitol Building Helena Mon tana Contractors are urged to view the site of the work and to check their bid carefully as no alterations or correc tions will be allowed after bids have been entered Each bid shall be accompanied by a certified check in the amount of 5 or more of the amount of the bid Check shall be made out to the State Treasur er Each bidder will be required to have a license from the Montana State Board of Equalization in a classification that will allow the bidder to execute the contract Bid checks of unsuccessful bidders will be returned as soon as award is made The"
